14:45.843 --> 14:47.094
{\an3}Well...

14:47.177 --> 14:49.597
She's Matt's wife
and, you know...

14:49.680 --> 14:51.974
{\an1}And she's in
a terrible situation.

14:52.057 --> 14:54.059
{\an1}One which
we can help her with.

14:54.143 --> 14:55.811
{\an3}We?

14:55.894 --> 14:58.480
