some contacts in Mexico

14:58.564 --> 15:00.274
who could get us clozapine.

15:00.357 --> 15:02.109
{\an1}And you have
the money to get it.

15:02.192 --> 15:03.277
Mm-hmm.

15:03.360 --> 15:04.695
What?

