15:58.290 --> 16:01.627
{\an1}To buy drugs,
uh, for Lauren.

16:01.710 --> 16:03.587
Oh, you guys are
going to Mexico?

16:03.671 --> 16:06.215
That sounds familiar.

16:06.298 --> 16:08.300
{\an1}Uh, but,
we're through here now

16:08.384 --> 16:10.427
