17:04.815 --> 17:05.941
Come here sit down, come on.

17:06.023 --> 17:08.026
Sit down, sit down, sit down.

17:08.109 --> 17:09.236
The voices, Steve.
The ones that are telling her

17:09.319 --> 17:10.445
she's a descendent
of Queen Elizabeth.

