17:33.719 --> 17:35.929
{\an3}Hey, don't sweat it.
I'm sorry.

17:36.013 --> 17:37.973
Sorry, man.

17:38.057 --> 17:40.100
{\an3}LAUREN:
Hey.

17:43.604 --> 17:45.606
Okay.

17:59.620 --> 18:00.954
(phone beeps off)

18:02.080 --> 18:04.416
{\an1}Ooh,<i> chicle.</i>
<i>Gracias, señor.</i>

18:04.500 --> 18:05.626
Still no answer.

