{\an1}Uh, he knows
we're coming, though.

18:07.711 --> 18:10.380
Maybe we should just go.

18:10.464 --> 18:12.132
Uh, maybe
this wasn't a good idea.

18:12.216 --> 18:13.383
{\an1}Oh, come on.
Spending the day in Mexico?

18:13.467 --> 18:15.719
Always a good idea.

18:15.803 --> 18:18.514
