21:53.145 --> 21:54.521
Whatever. It's your life.

21:54.604 --> 21:56.064
{\an3}Hmm?

21:56.148 --> 21:58.066
I'm just sayingith"--

21:58.150 --> 21:59.901
that the whole time
she was freaking out

21:59.985 --> 22:01.319
