I thought
we agreed not to do this.

29:59.464 --> 30:00.465
Wait a minute, Kel.

30:00.548 --> 30:02.717
You changed your mind.
I didn't change anything, okay?

30:02.800 --> 30:05.386
Your contact called, you were
out of the room, so I arranged

30:05.470 --> 30:08.723
a little meet and greet,
and, uh, I handled it.

30:08.806 --> 30:09.516
