30:09.599 --> 30:10.600
{\an1}'Cause I knew
you wouldn't approve.

30:10.683 --> 30:12.060
Just like our friendly

30:12.143 --> 30:13.853
neighborhood customs agent
back there.

30:13.937 --> 30:15.730
{\an1}That's why
I said all that

30:15.813 --> 30:16.606
stuff I said to him about us.

30:16.689 --> 30:18.191
Right.

30:18.274 --> 30:20.693
So you didn't mean any
of that stuff?

30:20.777 --> 30:22.695
About us, you know,

30:22.779 --> 30:23.530
our feelings?

30:23.613 --> 30:25.865
No... not a word.

30:25.949 --> 30:27.450
Good, good. Neither did I.

30:30.787 --> 30:32.539
DONNA:
<i>Gina and I caught up with Matt.</i>

30:32.622 --> 30:33.706
<i>He was</i>

30:33.790 --> 30:34.832
