30:34.916 --> 30:36.709
(gentle piano music plays)

30:36.793 --> 30:38.378
So, who's the trustee?

30:38.461 --> 30:40.547
{\an1}Gina doesn't know,
but according to Matt,

30:40.630 --> 30:42.549
it's probably the bank.

30:42.632 --> 30:44.884
Well, the bank's responsible
for how the money's spent.

30:44.968 --> 30:46.553
Or misspent.

30:46.636 --> 30:48.221
{\an1}So even though
Bobbi was irresponsible...

30:48.304 --> 30:50.098
{\an3}The bank's on the line
to pay her back,

30:50.181 --> 30:51.975
{\an3}and since the bank has
conveniently deep pockets,

30:52.058 --> 30:53.560
she should get
her money back.

30:53.643 --> 30:54.644
And more.

30:54.727 --> 30:57.230
And I told her she should go
for pain and suffering.

30:57.313 --> 30:58.773
Let's hope she handles it

30:58.856 --> 31:01.943
