sorry for the guy, fine.

31:19.752 --> 31:22.797
I just... I don't think
he treated you well.

31:22.880 --> 31:24.007
The point is

31:24.090 --> 31:25.508
that he's alone,
and we're together.

31:25.592 --> 31:27.510
That's what I'd like
to focus on--

31:27.594 --> 31:29.012
you and I being together.

31:30.054 --> 31:31.681
I know.
I just feel bad.

31:31.764 --> 31:33.933
Yeah, I know you do.

31:34.017 --> 31:36.185
He is a good guy,
and I hurt him.

31:36.269 --> 31:38.605
I'm sorry.

31:38.688 --> 31:39.480
It's okay.

31:39.564 --> 31:41.482
No.

31:41.566 --> 31:43.067
I really am sorry.

