31:59.751 --> 32:01.669
{\an1}You called me 15 times
to check on me.

32:01.753 --> 32:03.338
{\an3}I know, but four hours
for a continuance?

32:03.421 --> 32:05.173
{\an3}I'm sorry. I should never
have been gone so long.

32:05.256 --> 32:06.382
I am so sorry.

32:06.466 --> 32:07.675
