All right, come here.

32:18.770 --> 32:19.687
I'm sorry.

32:19.771 --> 32:21.648
(knocking)

32:21.731 --> 32:23.733
Oh.

32:26.944 --> 32:27.862
{\an1}Hey.

32:27.945 --> 32:29.197
Hi.

32:29.280 --> 32:30.615
Sorry it took us so long.

32:30.698 --> 32:32.742
Yeah, but, um...

32:32.825 --> 32:34.619
we got it.

32:36.788 --> 32:38.706
Hmm.

32:38.790 --> 32:40.708
That-That's great, right?

32:40.792 --> 32:43.503
{\an1}This way I'll have more time
to enjoy with Matt.

32:43.586 --> 32:45.213
I was glad to do it.

32:45.296 --> 32:46.881
{\an3}Yeah, if there's
anything else

32:46.964 --> 32:49.509
we can do...

32:49.592 --> 32:50.885
No, I-I think that's it.

32:50.968 --> 32:52.428
{\an1}MATT:
Yeah.

32:53.471 --> 32:55.473
This is all I need.

33:15.868 --> 33:16.744
Hey.

33:19.205 --> 33:21.082
Hey.

33:22.333 --> 33:25.962
If it's any consolation,
I'm really proud of you.

33:26.045 --> 33:28.548
It's gonna be okay, Janet.

33:36.681 --> 33:38.599
I don't have
any clean underwear.

33:38.683 --> 33:39.934
{\an1}Excuse me?

33:40.017 --> 33:42.270
Here. I don't have any.

33:42.353 --> 33:43.438
Oh.

33:43.521 --> 33:46.274
So I have to go home.

33:46.357 --> 33:50.111
{\an1}Oh.

33:50.194 --> 33:52.613
{\an1}Well, maybe your father
won't be there.

33:52.697 --> 33:56.617
After spending
the whole night out with you?

33:56.701 --> 33:58.619
He'll be there.

33:58.703 --> 34:02.623
{\an1}You did
the right thing, Janet.

34:02.707 --> 34:05.835
It's gonna be okay.

34:13.842 --> 34:15.969
What you said--

34:16.053 --> 34:18.973
{\an3}that part after
the Three Stooges.

34:19.056 --> 34:20.433
That my mom's gay?

34:23.895 --> 34:25.353
That I love you.

34:27.523 --> 34:29.442
Well, if you want
to take it back,

34:29.525 --> 34:30.610
right now would be the time.

34:30.693 --> 34:33.780
I don't want to take it back.

34:33.862 --> 34:35.447
Are you sure?

34:35.531 --> 34:38.868
I'm sure.

34:38.951 --> 34:41.496
