34:50.087 --> 34:52.465
{\an3}Gina, Gina.

34:52.547 --> 34:55.009
I'm late for work.

34:55.092 --> 34:58.304
Yeah, I just want
to say I'm sorry.

34:58.387 --> 34:59.388
{\an3}I shouldn't have
asked Dylan

34:59.472 --> 35:00.848
{\an3}to go down to Mexico
with me.

35:01.933 --> 35:04.811
We got the drugs.

35:04.894 --> 35:07.313
Oh.

35:07.396 --> 35:08.523
What, to kill the competition?

35:08.606 --> 35:11.692
I mean, what do you want me
to do say, "Congratulations"?

35:13.402 --> 35:15.154
Hi.

35:15.238 --> 35:17.532
Hey. I'm leaving.

35:17.615 --> 35:19.200
{\an1}Oh, I, uh, I was
just coming to see you.

35:19.283 --> 35:20.827
Sorry to disappoint you.

35:24.831 --> 35:26.332
She didn't look sorry.

35:26.415 --> 35:28.000
Are you going
to tell her what happened?

35:28.084 --> 35:31.420
No.

35:31.504 --> 35:32.588
You gonna tell Matt?

35:32.672 --> 35:35.258
I should, but no.

35:45.101 --> 35:48.020
You know how I was, uh, saying
that it was really nice

35:48.104 --> 35:49.730
to have something
to look forward to?

35:52.358 --> 35:53.359
It's nice, isn't it?

35:53.442 --> 35:59.031
I think it's enough to, uh, make
life worth living,

35:59.115 --> 36:00.616
no matter what.

36:12.712 --> 36:14.922
Are you sure
this is what you want?

36:15.006 --> 36:18.926
No.

36:20.052 --> 36:21.596
But it's what I'm gonna do.

36:21.679 --> 36:23.431
Okay, okay.

36:23.514 --> 36:24.640
Then-Then-Then
we'll move back to New York.

36:24.724 --> 36:26.100
I can get a job there.

36:26.183 --> 36:28.603
This way, I'll watch over
you as much as possible,

36:28.686 --> 36:31.105
and we'll go through this
together, okay?

36:31.188 --> 36:33.608
Really?

36:33.691 --> 36:35.735
Yeah.

36:43.534 --> 36:45.494
(upbeat rock and roll playing)

36:53.377 --> 36:55.296
{\an3}Hey.

36:55.379 --> 36:57.423
Hey.

36:59.091 --> 37:00.635
{\an3}YouI had...

37:00.718 --> 37:03.763
(both chuckle)

37:05.723 --> 37:06.766
Last night was nice.

37:06.849 --> 37:09.101
Yeah, it was really nice.

37:10.519 --> 37:12.980
I mean, considering the fact
it's been a while.

37:13.064 --> 37:15.608
Over a year.

37:15.691 --> 37:17.485
And the thing with Noah.

37:17.568 --> 37:21.989
Yeah, and-and you'd have to say
it went better than expected.

37:22.073 --> 37:23.866
Better than expected.

37:23.950 --> 37:25.952
Just what I was going for.

37:26.035 --> 37:26.953
