37:27.036 --> 37:29.205
Yeah, I think I do.

37:29.288 --> 37:31.415
Listen, that stuff with Noah...

37:32.833 --> 37:35.378
I just have a lot
of things to work out.

37:35.461 --> 37:37.129
Yeah, I know.

37:38.464 --> 37:40.341
Donna...

37:40.424 --> 37:42.218
really, I know.

37:48.432 --> 37:50.851
You talk to your father?

37:50.935 --> 37:52.979
Mmm. Well, what did he say?

37:53.062 --> 37:55.231
(heavy sigh)

37:55.314 --> 37:57.566
He said that he respected
my decision.

37:57.650 --> 37:58.651
Well, that's good.

37:58.734 --> 38:01.028
And he wants me to respect his.

38:01.112 --> 38:02.154
{\an1}His?

38:02.238 --> 38:03.990
What do you mean his?
It's your life.

38:04.073 --> 38:06.242
Yeah, but it's his house.

38:07.743 --> 38:10.746
And as long as I'm with you, he
doesn't want me living in it.

38:10.830 --> 38:11.914
He threw you out?

38:11.998 --> 38:15.668
{\an3}Yeah, as soon as I told him
that we loved each other.

38:15.751 --> 38:17.878
I can't believe that.

38:17.962 --> 38:20.506
That's so wrong.

38:20.589 --> 38:21.757
I'm so sorry.

38:42.695 --> 38:44.113
You were right, you know.

38:44.196 --> 38:46.615
About me being a hypocrite.

38:46.699 --> 38:48.159
Yeah, well, you're in
pretty good company.

38:48.242 --> 38:50.036
Everyone else is, too.

38:50.119 --> 38:52.663
Well, I should have told you
what really happened with David,

38:52.747 --> 38:53.748
and I'm sorry about that.

38:53.831 --> 38:56.959
All right.
You can tell me now.

38:57.043 --> 38:58.586
Okay.

38:58.669 --> 39:00.755
The photographer,
he pushed us together

39:00.838 --> 39:01.672
and asked us to kiss.

39:01.756 --> 39:02.631
{\an1}You're gonna blame this
on a photographer?

39:02.715 --> 39:05.634
{\an3}No. But I am saying
that it was impulsive.

39:05.718 --> 39:07.595
Okay, it sounds pretty
meaningless.

39:07.678 --> 39:08.637
Is that the case?

39:08.721 --> 39:11.390
No, it isn't.

39:13.642 --> 39:15.102
All right, where does
this leave us?

39:15.186 --> 39:17.605
I don't know.

39:23.694 --> 39:25.613
(knocking on door)

39:25.696 --> 39:27.615
(turns off music)

39:30.201 --> 39:31.118
{\an1}Kelly, hi.

39:31.202 --> 39:32.119
Hi.

39:32.203 --> 39:33.287
Thanks for coming.

39:33.370 --> 39:34.163
Is everything okay?

39:34.246 --> 39:36.123
Your message said
it was important.

39:37.875 --> 39:40.294
I want you to know how much
I appreciate what you did.

39:40.377 --> 39:45.466
{\an1}You put yourself at risk
to get me medicine.

39:45.549 --> 39:48.302
{\an1}But, uh...
I'm not gonna take it.

39:48.385 --> 39:50.137
Well, won't you
get sick again?

39:50.221 --> 39:54.809
Yeah, in some ways,
I already am.

39:54.892 --> 39:56.936
{\an1}But, um...

39:57.019 --> 39:59.438
{\an1}you know, maybe someday,
they'll find a cure,

39:59.522 --> 40:01.649
{\an1}and when they do,
I want to be first in line.

40:01.732 --> 40:04.610
I hope that you are.

40:04.693 --> 40:08.989
Um... listen,
I don't have much time,

40:09.073 --> 40:12.159
{\an3}so I'm just gonna
be blunt, okay?

40:12.243 --> 40:15.788
{\an1}I, um... I want you
to do me another favor.

40:15.871 --> 40:18.332
Okay. Anything.

40:18.415 --> 40:20.501
Take care of Matt.

40:20.584 --> 40:22.169
{\an3}Lauren...

40:22.253 --> 40:23.963
Watch over him.
Make him happy.

40:24.046 --> 40:27.716
{\an3}You will be able to do
that soon enough.

40:27.800 --> 40:31.011
I see the way he looks at you,

40:31.095 --> 40:34.181
{\an1}the way he smiles
when you walk in a room,

40:34.265 --> 40:36.350
{\an1}and, and I know that
he loves you very much.

40:36.433 --> 40:38.561
He loves you, too.

40:39.812 --> 40:41.730
Will you do this
for me, please?

40:41.814 --> 40:43.816
(door opens)

40:43.899 --> 40:45.860
Hey.

40:46.819 --> 40:48.571
What's going on?

40:48.654 --> 40:50.030
Kelly?

40:51.407 --> 40:53.409
Course... I will.

40:58.539 --> 41:01.000
Will what?

41:01.083 --> 41:03.252
Take care of you when I'm gone.

41:03.335 --> 41:05.588
{\an3}What... but I'm
going, too. What...?

41:05.671 --> 41:08.340
You offered and that's...

41:08.424 --> 41:09.675
that's very sweet.

41:09.758 --> 41:12.178
But...
that's not what you want.

41:12.261 --> 41:13.596
Yes, it is.

41:13.679 --> 41:14.597
But it's not what I want.

41:14.680 --> 41:16.849
Come with me and help me

41:16.932 --> 41:20.019
get settled,
but then come back here, Matt.

41:20.102 --> 41:22.104
Move on with your life
with Kelly.

41:23.355 --> 41:25.316
Promise me that.

41:25.399 --> 41:26.275
Lauren, I...

41:26.358 --> 41:27.818
{\an1}Please?

41:29.236 --> 41:30.571
I can't.

41:35.367 --> 41:38.078
Then promise me
that you'll be happy.

41:50.841 --> 41:51.884
(door opens)

41:53.886 --> 41:55.471
{\an3}Hey.

41:55.554 --> 41:56.764
I'm really glad you're here.

41:56.847 --> 41:58.432
Hey.
Uh, what's going on?

41:58.515 --> 42:00.476
Did you find out the name
of the trustee?

42:00.559 --> 42:03.437
No, but my mom's in my room,

42:03.520 --> 42:05.773
so I'm gonna go ask her
right now.

42:05.856 --> 42:06.774
Want to come?

42:06.857 --> 42:08.234
Yeah.

42:08.317 --> 42:12.446
Well... this is gonna sound
kind of crazy,

42:12.529 --> 42:15.115
but I just need your support.

42:15.199 --> 42:19.119
You know, I'm, I'm really sorry
that you're going through this,

42:19.203 --> 42:21.288
but in a weird sort of way,

42:21.372 --> 42:23.457
I feel like this stuff
with your mom has

42:23.540 --> 42:25.000
kind of brought us together.

42:25.084 --> 42:26.919
{\an1}And I know
it's no consolation,

42:27.002 --> 42:29.755
but it feels a lot better.

42:31.340 --> 42:32.800
I'm glad you feel that way.

42:32.883 --> 42:34.635
{\an3}All right.

42:34.718 --> 42:36.470
Let's go find out
whose deep pockets

42:36.553 --> 42:37.638
{\an1}you're gonna be
digging into.

42:37.721 --> 42:38.973
Okay.

42:39.056 --> 42:39.640
{\an1}(laughs)
No.

42:39.723 --> 42:42.476
No, I don't.

42:42.559 --> 42:44.311
{\an1}Oh, I got
to call you back

42:44.395 --> 42:47.189
If you're here
to talk about the trust...

42:47.273 --> 42:48.774
{\an1}We're going to talk
about the trust.

42:48.857 --> 42:50.651
Calmly this time.

42:50.734 --> 42:53.487
Yeah, just...

42:53.570 --> 42:54.488
for one second, Mom,

42:54.571 --> 42:57.199
{\an1}I'm gonna forget everything
you've done to me

42:57.283 --> 42:59.868
{\an1}and I just want you to tell me
who the trustee is.

42:59.952 --> 43:01.161
No, you don't.

43:01.245 --> 43:02.329
Well, we've been told

43:02.413 --> 43:04.665
that the trustee is the person
who's legally responsible

43:04.748 --> 43:06.667
